      "content": "i mean i dont really have asthma or anything, i just get really sneezy and stuff when the pollen is high. the wheezing is probably just because i'm out of breath from running around. if i just take the zyrtec now, will that fix the wheezing too? i really dont want to go to a doctor if i can just help it myself",
